00:11:25.000 --> 00:11:29.000
Now, for starters let me clear up,  I'll take five minutes to clear up,   

00:11:29.000 --> 00:11:33.000
four minutes to clear up some misconceptions about Mendel.   

00:11:33.000 --> 00:11:37.000
It has generally been written that Mendel was this monk working in this  

00:11:37.000 --> 00:11:41.000
monastery often in the Chez Republic,  at that point in the  

00:11:41.000 --> 00:11:45.000
Austro-Hungarian Empire,  and he was isolated, working by  

00:11:45.000 --> 00:11:50.000
