00:14:18.000 --> 00:14:22.000
in fact, apples and grapes, the Pomological and Enological Society  

00:14:22.000 --> 00:14:26.000
of Braunau was organized.  Braunau being the capital of the  

00:14:26.000 --> 00:14:30.000
